Congratulations Sir/Madam Wizard
 
     You have now become an apprentice wizard by reaching level 100.
To become a full wizard (level 102) you need to do several things.
First, read all the docs.  and second, after completeing the doc reading,
you will be given an interview by a ARCH or higher.  If, after the
interview, the ARCH feels that you would be an asset to Darkwind, you
will be sponsored to Wizard status and given coding abilities.
 
     Your repertoire of commands have now been extended with some new
wizards commmands. You can get help for those by typeing 'help wizard'.
These new powers MUST be used sensibly! From now on you are bound by the
rules that you will find by typing the command 'read rules'. Do this as
your first action when you stop reading this text.
 
     To help you get started there is another file that you can read. It
will introduce you to the new world of Darkwind and help you make a workroom
among other things.  AFTER becoming a full Wizard, YOU MUST HAVE A WORKROOM 
BEFORE YOU CAN QUIT!!! So make sure you have one!! You will get errors and
not be allowed to quit if you try and quit without one, so this is very
important!
 
                Good luck!
 
